mah","tag-agreed-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-disease-al-daa","tag-health","tag-manners-adab","tag-plague-al-taun","tag-sickness-al-marad","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8QW","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/13\/believers-die-plague-martyrs\/","url_meta":{"origin":34034,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Pestilence: Believers who die by plague are martyrs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: She asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, about plagues, and he said, \u201cIt is a punishment that Allah sends upon whomever He wills, but Allah has made it mercy for the believers. Any servant who resides in a land afflicted by plague, remaining\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14057,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/08\/five-martyrs\/","url_meta":{"origin":34034,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Martyrdom: Five types of martyrs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe martyrs are five kinds: one who dies of plague, one who dies of stomach infection, one who drowns, one who dies under debris, and one who dies in the way of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14061,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/08\/who-is-a-martyr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34034,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Martyrs: Who do you consider your martyrs?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWho do you consider a martyr among you?\u201d They said, \u201cThe one who is killed in the way of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIf that were so, there are few martyrs in my nation.\u201d They said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32734,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/11\/seven-martyrs-besides-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":34034,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shahid: Seven types of martyrdom besides fighting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn \u2018Atik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are seven martyrs besides one who is killed in the way of Allah: the victim of plague is a martyr, the one who drowns is a martyr, the one who dies of chest pain\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25473,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/29\/wash-vessels-kuffar-pork-khamr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34034,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Utensils: Wash vessels of unbelievers if they eat pork, drink wine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Tha\u2019labah reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, we live in a land of the people of the Book. Can we eat from their utensils?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not eat from them unless you cannot find anything else, then wash them and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15500,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/startle-surprise-scare-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":34034,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Do not surprise family in the night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you is absent for a long time while traveling, let him not startle his family in the night upon his return.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5244, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 715 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34034","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithon